          <Icon name="tabler:code" class="h-5 w-5 text-white/80" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Open & transparent</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed text-white/70">
            Fully open-source using transparent, with many stargazers on GitHub. Audit and customize everything.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="relative py-10 pr-8 md:pr-16 md:odd:pr-16 md:odd:before:absolute md:odd:before:top-[20%] md:odd:before:right-0 md:odd:before:bottom-[20%] md:odd:before:w-px md:odd:before:bg-gradient-to-b md:odd:before:from-transparent md:odd:before:via-white/10 md:odd:before:to-transparent md:odd:before:content-[''] md:even:pl-16"
    >
      <div class="flex items-start">
        <div class="mt-0.5 mr-6 flex h-9 w-9 min-w-9 items-center justify-center rounded bg-white/5">
          <Icon name="tabler:scale" class="h-5 w-5 text-white/80" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Legal & reversible</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed text-white/70">
            Complies with Microsoft's terms (no ISO redistribution). Peace of mind when using AtlasOS.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
